(4, 3, 43, 49, 3, '69.35.200.251', 1412299156, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Play with the staff', 'What better leader of a public thing is better than one that joins the people in merrymaking and such? Well the staff here being gamers and fun lovers ourselves so we will occasionally join you guys in various games be they Showdown, Minecraft, Battlefield, etc. Some of us will even put together tournaments for certain games. We try to pick games that are free, or are easy to obtain so that you can join us easily and vice versa. So if you wanna play with the staff let us know by reply to this thread with what game you wanna play with us.', 'ae6cabe4139f6a91a9e44959cbdd96aa', 0, '', 'lniybm6z', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
