(6, 4, 25, 2, 0, '199.116.102.191', 1412301047, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'I am Le Pug!', 'Well just so I can give an example, I will introduce myself. I''m Le pug, creator of the hack [i:2d3m78ug]Pokmon: Discovery[/i:2d3m78ug]. \nI enjoy ROM hacking a lot. It has taken up most of my free time actually lol. When I''m not doing this, I''m either working for the US Navy on my ship the USS Georgia or I''m hanging out with my wife! If you''re wondering, the name is because I have two pugs for pets. Initially named after my black dog, Ling Ling. Yes... Ling Ling. They''re Chinese dogs alright, jeez! Anyways...\n\nHope I get to know everyone who joins and if you have anything for me, feel free to PM me or whatever. Hope you enjoy the site!', '8539aae61eedb7f7d811739b6f3ad5b2', 0, 'IA==', '2d3m78ug', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
