(36, 23, 44, 52, 5, '74.104.118.193', 1412376772, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Rules and Regulations', '[color=#800080:c3wfqlt9][center:c3wfqlt9][size=150:c3wfqlt9][b:c3wfqlt9][u:c3wfqlt9][i:c3wfqlt9]Rules and Regulations[/i:c3wfqlt9][/u:c3wfqlt9][/b:c3wfqlt9][/size:c3wfqlt9][/center:c3wfqlt9]\n\n\n[i:c3wfqlt9]Here at the Let''s Play section, you will find all things concerning walkthroughs, challenges, and let''s plays. First, I''d like to go over a few ground rules~\n[/i:c3wfqlt9]\n[center:c3wfqlt9][b:c3wfqlt9][i:c3wfqlt9]1. [u:c3wfqlt9]Don&#39;t be rude and treat others the way you want to be treated[/u:c3wfqlt9]: This should be self explanatory, you can not be rude and talk bad about people doing let&#39;s plays/walkthroughs/challenges and the developers of the hack you are playing, which means you can&#39;t be like &quot;this sux the creator needs to die&quot;. This leads me to the next rule...\n\n2.[u:c3wfqlt9] Constructive criticism is allowed[/u:c3wfqlt9]: What this means is that you can criticize a rom-hack or actual game and you have to explain why it is good or bad. If I see criticism which is not constructive &#40;meaning you pretty much just say &quot;this sux&quot;&#41; your posts will be deleted. If the injury is repeated multiple times, you will get a warning and so on.\n\n3. [u:c3wfqlt9]While any game or hack let&#39;s play is allowed, you must make it clear on what audience you are targeting[/u:c3wfqlt9]: Meaning, you can say explicit things and play mature games in your videos, just make sure you are going to get 18+ audience instead of 17 and under.\n\n4.[u:c3wfqlt9] All challenges are allowed[/u:c3wfqlt9]: Yes, so if you guys like Pokemon challenges and other game challenges, you can post them here and even make your own challenge!\n\n5. [u:c3wfqlt9]You are allowed to post videos or do a written let&#39;s play[/u:c3wfqlt9]: A video should at least be around 5-10 minutes long or higher, and there will be a limit to the amount of pictures you can post, I would roughly say you are allowed to post at least 10 - 45 pictures in each post for your let&#39;s play/walkthrough/challenge. You can also put all your videos/posts in spoilers on your main post for the created thread too.\n\n6. [u:c3wfqlt9]We are not advertising your youtube or twitch accounts[/u:c3wfqlt9]: Pretty much, don&#39;t advertise your youtube or twitch accounts here, if I see anything that falls under an advertisement it will be deleted.[/i:c3wfqlt9][/b:c3wfqlt9][/center:c3wfqlt9]\n[i:c3wfqlt9]So have fun and let the games begin~[/i:c3wfqlt9][/color:c3wfqlt9]', 'e4f3e97ad69b8c642f8f5f0697edfc5a', 0, 'ZwQ=', 'c3wfqlt9', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(37, 24, 31, 52, 0, '74.104.118.193', 1412378692, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Discussion Rules', '[color=#8000BF:315pmrrw][size=150:315pmrrw][center:315pmrrw][b:315pmrrw][i:315pmrrw][u:315pmrrw]Discussion Rules[/u:315pmrrw][/i:315pmrrw][/b:315pmrrw][/center:315pmrrw][/size:315pmrrw]\n\n\n\n[i:315pmrrw]In this section of the forums, you can have rom-hacking related discussions, here are some ground rules~\n\n[center:315pmrrw][b:315pmrrw]1.[u:315pmrrw] Be friendly[/u:315pmrrw]: Don&#39;t start trouble and cause fights or downright be rude to others. If I see anyone being really rude, I will delete posts on sight and repeated injury will make me give you a warning. I don&#39;t want to be that guy.\n\n2. [u:315pmrrw]No questions[/u:315pmrrw]: Well, you can ask questions, but opinionated questions. In other words, this is not a help section, this is just used to discuss rom-hacking in general.\n\n3. [u:315pmrrw]No spam[/u:315pmrrw]: This should be a golden rule. Spam is advertising, saying a one word post, being rude, being a troll, etc..I will not condone this behavior so I will still delete posts on sight.\n\n4. [u:315pmrrw]Mild Swearing[/u:315pmrrw]: This is a PG-13 site, you can say some swears if you must, but strong language such as &quot;fu#k&quot; or &quot;cu#t&quot; is not allowed. Don&#39;t censor words either like I just did, that was an example of words not to say.\n\n5. [u:315pmrrw]If you want to &quot;debate&quot; take it to PM&#39;s[/u:315pmrrw]: Obviously, people are going to have different opinions, I can&#39;t stop that, but, if you guys must &quot;debate&quot;, take it away from the thread it is on, it&#39;s a distraction.\n[/b:315pmrrw][/center:315pmrrw]\nDiscuss! ~[/i:315pmrrw][/color:315pmrrw]', '9068718d4af7f4a6104f5b458b1db2d1', 0, 'ZwQ=', '315pmrrw', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0);
