(38, 25, 31, 52, 0, '74.104.118.193', 1412380687, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Map Rating Thread', '[color=#8000BF:lmslsgky][size=150:lmslsgky][b:lmslsgky][u:lmslsgky][i:lmslsgky][center:lmslsgky]The Map Rating Thread[/center:lmslsgky][/i:lmslsgky][/u:lmslsgky][/b:lmslsgky][/size:lmslsgky]\n\n[b:lmslsgky][i:lmslsgky]Over here, although it''s neither a discussion or a competition thread, is going to be very handy for people that want to map and make rom-hacks or actual games in general. Just upload a picture of your map and someone or a few people will constructively criticize it. So here''s some rules and remember to enjoy this thread and take in the knowledge others are imparting on to you:[/i:lmslsgky][/b:lmslsgky]\n\n[b:lmslsgky][i:lmslsgky]1.[u:lmslsgky] Don''t be rude[/u:lmslsgky]: Show people respect.\n\n2.[u:lmslsgky] Constructive Criticism is allowed[/u:lmslsgky]: You can say what''s right or wrong with the maps in a friendly manor.\n\n3. [u:lmslsgky]No Spam or Advertisements[/u:lmslsgky]: Automatic post delete.[/i:lmslsgky][/b:lmslsgky][/color:lmslsgky]', 'b753f675e929bd5b2fc3af693ba18ffd', 0, 'ZwQ=', 'lmslsgky', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
