(40, 27, 32, 51, 0, '66.176.179.102', 1412381112, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'The Learning Lobby Rules', 'The Learning Lobby is a section of the forum where people can post tutorials to help others, and ask for help, by making a thread in the Tutorials section, or asking for help in the &quot;Simple Questions&quot; thread if it''s a simple question, or creating a topic if it''s a bigger issue you need assistance with. Either way, our members and staff will be glad to assist you.\n\nRules:\n[list:gimfdend]Follow all rules, whether they be this section''s, or the forums.\n\nWait 12 hours before making a double post, if you have to.\n\nTry to search first before asking.\n\nIf there is an active tutorial on the subject you need assistance with, ask there, rather than make a thread or post in the Simple Questions thread. If after a day or two, you receive no answer, feel free to make a post, or a topic.\n\nBe descriptive with your problems. Don''t make posts simply stating your problem, without describing it. For example, if you are having issues with a script, post the scripts, and try to provide screenshots for better assistance.[/list:u:gimfdend]\n\nIf you need assistance, contact me or any Super Moderator or Administrator.\n\n\nThese rules may eventually change, and if they do, we will do our best to notify our users when we do.', '647b4103d6eee923bb26ad27a232aeb3', 0, 'AEA=', 'gimfdend', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
