(52, 30, 26, 2, 0, '199.116.102.191', 1412392704, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Global Rules and Guidelines', '[size=90:3lqtwmkg]In order to make your and everyone else''s experience on Poktch a pleasant one, please follow these rules that outline what is acceptable behavior. We have designed these rules in order to minimize conflict and maximize your enjoyment of the site. Our Moderators have the authority to enforce such rules and act on behalf of your and Poktch''s best interests.[/size:3lqtwmkg]\n\n[size=150:3lqtwmkg]Interacting with Other Users on Poktch:[/size:3lqtwmkg]\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]No Spamming Outside the Chatterbox Forum:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Spam, or posts that are nonsensical or irrelevant to the forum in which they''re posted, should only be posted in the [i:3lqtwmkg]Chatterbox[/i:3lqtwmkg] forum. Users are encouraged to stay on topic and be relevant to the theme of where discussions are held. Being informative or entertaining are also good ways to get a good conversation going. [i:3lqtwmkg]Bumping isn''t considered spam.[/i:3lqtwmkg]\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Be Courteous:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Please be civil and courteous towards your fellow Poktchians. We have a very liberal policy regarding language, but overly abusive language is not permitted. If your post is excessively vulgar, insulting, explicit, or hateful, it may be removed and disciplinary actions may be taken on your account. Do not try and bypass the word censorship either. Doing so will result in warnings that will vary in penalty.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]No Trolling:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Posting material that is inflammatory or intended solely to offend or provoke other members is called ''trolling'', and is not permitted.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]No Stalking:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Persistent harassment of an individual or group of individuals against their wishes (commonly known as ''stalking'') is not permitted. If someone asks you to stop, please leave them alone. This goes for users who wish to not be bothered with private messaging.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Respect the TOS:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Encouraging or endorsing violations of our Terms of Service, or illicit activities in general, is not permitted.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Be Constructive:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] When commenting on artwork or reviewing web links, threads, tutorials, etc., please try to be constructive in your criticism or balance criticism with praise. If your comments are excessively insulting or vulgar, action may be taken against your account.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]No Cybering:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Soliciting or engaging in cybersex (exchanging descriptions of sexual experiences) or mature content role play is not allowed on Poktch. Making sexually suggestive or explicit posts can result in them being removed, and action being taken against your account.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]No Child Abuse:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Discussion, depiction or promotion of child sexuality, abuse, exploitation and/or related topics that may be harmful to or threaten the security of a child or minor is not allowed. Submitting any content or utilizing language or terms meant to imply or insinuate these situations may result in action being taken against your account.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Pirating:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Allowed but only in terms of anything Pokmon-related and that is in good taste. You may share saves, patches, images, etc. Pirating of movies, tv shows, and music is not acceptable on this forum.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Banking Services:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Unlike most forums, Poktch condones the use of banking services. If you want to draw art for money or auctions, create ASM routines for money, etc. go right ahead. It will be kept in moderation though and all transactions should be reviewed by a Moderator. Poktch reserves the right to disallow the user the right to banking services and take actions against your account. There are some items that you can not sell such as pirated games, movies, music, shows, etc. For more information, visit the [i:3lqtwmkg]Banking Services[/i:3lqtwmkg] forum.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]If In Doubt, Ask:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] If you are submitting content to Poktch and you are unsure whether that content violates our Terms of Service or other rules and guidelines, it is best to check with a Poktch Moderator before submission.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Money Links:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Monetized-using links in the forum is prohibited.\n\n[size=150:3lqtwmkg]Account:[/size:3lqtwmkg]\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Username Requirements:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] A-Z, 0-9, spaces, and all other normal characters are allowed. No upside down text, &quot;demonic&quot; text, or any hidden characters are allowed.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Name Changes:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] After registration, you are entitled to three name changes for free per year. After that, you will have to pay $1.00 per name change overage charge (all collected amount will be donated to charity).\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Sock-puppeting:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] You are not allowed to create more than one account under different personalities or evade a ban or suspension. If there is suspicion that you are doing so, you will be suspended until further notice.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Member Bans:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] The Poktch Staff are not obligated to share information regarding bans that have occurred to other members. \n\n[size=150:3lqtwmkg]Images:[/size:3lqtwmkg]\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Signatures:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Please keep signatures less than 500 pixels in size in height. Your ability to post signatures may be removed if you do not comply with this standard. Each situation will be a case by case situation.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Mature material:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Any material that is sexually explicit or pornographic, or depicts excessive violence or gore is not permitted. Tasteful nudity in the art forums is allowed on a case-by-case basis, but on the whole, it is a good idea to cater to a range of audiences. Keep in mind that some members may be as young as 10.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Harmful Images:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Certain types of graphic images may contribute to or otherwise cause viewers to experience an adverse physical reaction, such as migraine headaches or seizures, and are not permitted. Should your post or signature contain such an image, it may be removed.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg][u:3lqtwmkg]Copyright Violation:[/u:3lqtwmkg][/b:3lqtwmkg] Claiming art that you did not create yourself as your own work will be treated as art theft, which can result in legal prosecution in real life if used for profit. Attempting to use stolen art for profit is considered to be scamming. Additionally, art that you have made yourself, but that was heavily copied or traced from the work of others, or includes images or graphics you did not make yourself, may also be treated as art theft if the proper credits aren''t given. Make sure you credit those who you use images from. Permission is always nice to have also.\n\n[size=150:3lqtwmkg]Repercussions:[/size:3lqtwmkg]\n\n[warning:3lqtwmkg][size=127:3lqtwmkg]Failure to follow the rules above may result in your account being banned from Poktch. In some cases, the ban will be temporary, with repeat offenders receiving a permanent ban, and some cases may result in a permanent ban immediately. The following offenses are also grounds for an immediate permanent ban:[/size:3lqtwmkg][/warning:3lqtwmkg]\n\n[u:3lqtwmkg][color=#FF0040:3lqtwmkg]Scamming[/color:3lqtwmkg][/u:3lqtwmkg]. Any sort of scam involving files or money is grounds for an automatic ban of the most extreme. In some cases, it can lead to legal prosecution.\n\n[u:3lqtwmkg][color=#FF0040:3lqtwmkg]Hacking[/color:3lqtwmkg].[/u:3lqtwmkg] Hacking is defined as &quot;unauthorized access to another user''s account&quot;. This includes accessing an account that does not belong to you, or profiting from items taken from a hacked account. Attempts to hack, such as trying to obtain another user''s password, will also lead to your account being banned.\n\n[u:3lqtwmkg][color=#FF0040:3lqtwmkg]Impersonating[/color:3lqtwmkg][/u:3lqtwmkg] another user or Poktch Staff Member, including Administrators and Moderators.\n\n[u:3lqtwmkg][color=#FF0040:3lqtwmkg]Exploiting[/color:3lqtwmkg][/u:3lqtwmkg] site glitches for personal gain. No site is perfect, and you will (rarely) run into a glitch while using Poktch. When you do, please report it by posting to our [i:3lqtwmkg]Bug Reports[/i:3lqtwmkg] forum. However, intentionally exploiting obvious glitches in order to gain more items, Gold, or other benefits can result in your account being banned.\n\nPlease be aware that if your account is banned, you will no longer be able to access your Poktch purchases from the site.\n\n[b:3lqtwmkg]Every violation listed above that is taken into account will be posted as a warning against your account. Once you reach five warnings, your account will be suspended for one week. If you reach ten warnings, your account will be suspended for 90 days. If you reach fifteen warnings, your account will be banned to the most extreme. Note that certain violations may warrant more than one warning ticket.[/b:3lqtwmkg]\n\nFailure to comply with these rules and guidelines may result in disciplinary action and ultimately the termination of your Poktch account. Your use of Poktch is also subject to the terms and conditions set forth in the Terms of Service.', 'e7f61c2227809db9e2dc8702d01952c8', 0, 'ZwAACA==', '3lqtwmkg', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
